## ğŸ¨ Themes

### Light Theme (Default)
- Clean, bright interface with green accents
- Perfect for daytime gaming sessions

### Dark Mint Theme
- Soothing dark mint green color scheme
- Easy on the eyes for extended play
- Reduced eye strain in low-light environments

Toggle between themes using the button in the top-right corner. Your preference is automatically saved.

